    dc:description "Fig. 12. Distal portion of ovipositor, dorsal view. A. Cimmerosiro krivolutskyi gen. et sp. nov. (CIK). B. C. juberthiei gen. et sp. nov. (MHNG). C. C. rhodiensis gen. et sp. nov. (CIK). Scale bar = 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10656553/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10656525>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. A–E. Prosessus sensitif on telotarsus of leg I. A–B. Ebrosiro coiffaiti (Juberthie, 1956) gen. et comb. nov., male (CIK). C. E. coifaitii, female (CIK). D. Cimmerosiro krivolutskyi gen. et sp. nov., female (CIK). E. C. krivolutskyi gen. et sp. nov., male (CIK). F. C. rhodiensis gen. et sp. nov., female, genital orifice (CIK)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10656525/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

